    "description": "<p><strong>The future is calling. Will you answer? </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>At KLA-Tencor, we’re making technology advancements that are bigger—and tinier—than the world has ever seen. We research, develop and manufacture the world’s most advanced inspection and measurement equipment for the semiconductor and nanoelectronics industries. We’re passionate about creating solutions that drive progress and transform entire industries.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe innovation can come from anywhere. So whether you’re a seasoned scientist or a new college graduate, if you’re looking to solve problems and improve how the world works, you’ll have the opportunity to do it at KLA-Tencor. </p>\r\n",
